Text: Forgot to say I'd originally got this from some where in http://archive.org/details/etree  The concert info's in there, but I can't find it again. Sorry Floyd fans.

WOW. My first post and not one gee thank ya for a pink floyd concert that's never see the light of day before. Do you think I'll share the real rare stuff with you? keep holding your breath I'm working on it.

Thank you so much for uploading this!  People never take the time to say thank you, nor seed.

I had tickets for this show, but our car broke down.  By the time we made it from Olympia to Seattle, hitchhiking, there was only about fifteen minutes left of the show, and they wouldn't let us in.  So pissed.  I was 16 years old then, and I never had the chance to see them in concert.

I appreciate you taking the time to put this up for us, and I am sorry that more people didn't say "thanks".  People suck, sometimes.  :)
